edu.purdue.cs59000.umltranslator

Class UMLSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.purdue.cs59000.umltranslator.UMLSymbol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasCodeHandler, HasSource, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UMLActivationBox, UMLActor, UMLClass, UMLContainer, UMLLifeline, UMLMessage

    public abstract class UMLSymbol
extends java.lang.Object
implements HasSource, HasCodeHandler, java.io.Serializable
    UMLSymbol is an abstract class that all UML symbol representations inherit from. They all have a source, which is used to access the class from which messages are invoked or defined by.
    Author:
    Steve Yarusinsky
